import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import TypeNav from '@/pages/Home/TypeNav'
// TypeNav注册为全局组件,方便复用
import router from '@/router'
import {reqCategoryList} from '@/api'

Vue.config.productionTip = false

Vue.component(TypeNav.name,TypeNav)
reqCategoryList()
new Vue({
  render: h => h(App),
  router
}).$mount('#app')
